⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Doublethink
node 1984 · 1984 · ⟦Doublethink:1984:c83ca6⟧

WHO   — Doublethink — two beliefs, both held
WHAT  — The mental survival skill of Oceania: to know and not know, to lie and believe the lie, as the Party requires.
WHERE — 1984 · 1984  Framework inputs: Nineteen Eighty-Four (George Orwell, 1949)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because a regime built on contradiction needs minds that no longer demand consistency or truth.
HOW   — By disciplined self-deception — believing ‘2+2=5’ when ordered, then forgetting one ever believed otherwise.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am how you hold ‘War is Peace’ without flinching — the trick of believing the lie so completely you forget it was ever one.

